{"tid":1550214,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］肥媽首歌好成功","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T02:15:16.000Z","uid":307982,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b6b561847ead0de52b5f5d2f0d6d342343e703ce","tid":1550214,"uid":307982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:03:20.000Z","msg":"我岩岩係廳到播首歌啦<br />\n然後我個紅底阿婆聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問我肥媽係咪黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我答佢係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢依家信左首歌真係肥媽唱<br />\n仲鬧佢死漢奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n菲律賓人黎香港搵食仲要搞亂香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0efc8d1acdfad19b2a03135fad7a149184cc088","tid":1550214,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b2bdfe016f2d9f8af7eeee846286eb330609584","tid":1550214,"uid":123914,"like